title: Top L-L Highlights of the Week
text:
Top L-L Highlights of the Week 
By John Buffone 
jbuffone@gametimepa.com @jdbuffone on Twitter Posted: 10/24/2015 02:38:20 PM EDT 
As the league playoffs concluded and football season began its final push, this week's rundown is full of game-winners and explosive plays. 
5. Damon Camacho's 49-yard TD run vs Cocalico. 
4. Donegal's Mackenzie Allessie scores game-winning goal vs Penn Manor in the L-L field hockey finals. 
3. Cocalico's DJ Fabiani makes an interception right before halftime. 
2. Manheim Central pulls off a reverse pass to score on a two-point play to tie the game. 
1. Conestoga Valley freshman Juliana Bedoya scores in OT vs Hempfield in the L-L soccer semifinals. The Conestoga Valley girls' soccer team celebrated their OT win over Hempfield in the L-L semifinals.
